    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. This example demonstrates robust mechanical health, with the high-revving valvetrain operating seamlessly through the 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural rigidity during high-lateral-G cornering. The factory limited-slip differential delivers consistent torque bias, while the suspension bushings and dampers remain taut, ensuring the communicative steering feel inherent to the chassis. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this M3 offers a pure, analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
